data.description: Ideally situated on an oversized corner lot w/newer roof and 2023 new septic system! Decorative entry door w/cut glass insert opens to the defined entry hall w/ wood laminate flooring. You'll love the updated kitchen w/soft close cabinetry finished in a classic walnut. Of course soft close drawers too, SS appliances, and granite counters with a glass tile backsplash. The kitchen is open to a large family rm with soaring vaulted ceilings, SGD to porch and pool, and a romantic raised hearth, stone faced, wood burning fireplace! Large primary suite also offers vaulted ceilings & plush carpeting. Updated primary bath offers a double sink vanity w/granite counters, soft close cabinets and drawers and quality Moen fixtures. Extra deep soaking tub plus a separate frameless glass enclosed shower! Glass enclosed shower has river rock flooring and a river rock waterfall accent in the tile work. Spacious 4th bedroom w/ceiling fan and vaulted ceiling. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are both large and have ceiling fans. The guest bath is updated w/frameless glass shower enclosure, with a wave tile surround and a seat! There's also a 6 drawer, 2 cabinet vanity with granite counter and undermount sink. Huge back porch w/2 ceiling fans and lovely screen enclosed pool! Additionally, there's a large brick paver area with a fire pit. Backyard storage shed keeps your attached 2 car garage free for your vehicles! Truly a great home with lots of updates. All the big ticket items have been done. Don't miss this opportunity!
